These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, thai, argentine, canadian
4 different pets are kept: hamster, chinchilla, mouse, guinea-pig
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, gardening, puzzles, writing
4 different games are played: chess, canasta, billiard, whist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, funk, r&b
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, ebony, ivory, coral
 1. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
 2. the argentine is the fan of classical##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the canadian is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 6. the thai is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the person playing billiard is between the person who likes chestnut and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the right of the person playing chess##1
10. the person who likes chestnut is between the person playing billiard and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
11. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
12. the person playing whist is the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the fan of funk is between the fan of dubstep and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Nationality      | canadian        | thai       | argentine  | malaysian |
| Pet          | guinea-pig     | mouse         | chinchilla     | hamster    |
| Hobby         | gardening  | fishing      | puzzles   | writing     |
| Game           | canasta | chess | billiard   | whist     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | funk         | classical | r&b         |
| Color         | coral     | chestnut     | ebony  | ivory       |

