 2. the pakistani is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the canadian##1
 4. the german is between the person eating grapefruit and the person who's birthday is in january##2
 5. the person playing backgammon is the person eating pumpkin##1
 6. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 9. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
11. the person playing backgammon is the person who's sport is parkour##1
12. the person eating kale is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
13. the malaysian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
14. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the german##1

